result.name: New Island Cafe

reviews.text:
Excellent cafe, nice environment, good food (if you can get past the meat even in veggie dishes) and good service.
The location is amazing and like the whole of Hong Kong, its vibrant and colourful.

A cafe for locals which is right up my street! Me, the wife and kids stumbled upon this place on our first night in HK. Loved it. It is a quintessential Kowloon cafe, with s typical menu. We tried 4 main dishes as well as noodles and egg fried rice and wasn't disappointed. The drinks were nice too.
Original Hong Kong dishes!! A taste is intensive and delicious. Good treat! Thats why I like to come here when I get in Hong kong.
Staff spoke English and service was fast. Must try their magazine-famous wonton and fish balls noodles!! Food tasted excellent. Might be hard to find, in a older building but newly renovated.

My favourite place to go for Mixian! I tried the combination with all three - beef tendon, beef brisket and beef stomach and it's really delicious! The milk tea is also good! A cheaper place to eat in tst before going back to shop at the nearby HarbourCity!

result.name: 新金島魚蛋王

reviews.text:
Excellent cafe, nice environment, good food (if you can get past the meat even in veggie dishes) and good service.
The location is amazing and like the whole of Hong Kong, its vibrant and colourful.

37香港ドルで、美味しい海老ワンタン麺が食べられるのでオススメ！！
ビルの４階にあるので、呼び込みのおばさんについていかないとわかりにくいかも。
這里是尖沙咀的新金島魚蛋王，論設計和格局比較時尚，衛生整潔，職員服務熱情有禮。
ランチで良く利用します。出前一丁がなかなか旨く感じる。ミルクティーは超甘い。
